text: Brittany Furlan (born September 5, 1986 in Pennsylvania) is an American comedian and internet celebrity who is based in Los Angeles. She is best known for her work on the video sharing website, Vine. She is the most followed female on the website. Also, Time magazine has named her to be one of the most influential people on the internet. == References == == Other websites == * Vine website Category:1986 births Category:Comedians from Pennsylvania Category:American Internet celebrities Category:Living people
